11#ifndef MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_VAD_POLE_ZERO_FILTER_H_
12#define MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_VAD_POLE_ZERO_FILTER_H_
13
14#include <stddef.h>
15#include <stdint.h>
16
17namespace webrtc {
18
19class PoleZeroFilter {
20 public:
21 ~PoleZeroFilter() {}
22
23 static PoleZeroFilter* Create(const float* numerator_coefficients,
24 size_t order_numerator,
25 const float* denominator_coefficients,
26 size_t order_denominator);
27
28 int Filter(const int16_t* in, size_t num_input_samples, float* output);
29
30 private:
31 PoleZeroFilter(const float* numerator_coefficients,
32 size_t order_numerator,
33 const float* denominator_coefficients,
34 size_t order_denominator);
35
36 static const int kMaxFilterOrder = 24;
37
38 int16_t past_input_[kMaxFilterOrder * 2];
39 float past_output_[kMaxFilterOrder * 2];
40
41 float numerator_coefficients_[kMaxFilterOrder + 1];
42 float denominator_coefficients_[kMaxFilterOrder + 1];
43
44 size_t order_numerator_;
45 size_t order_denominator_;
46 size_t highest_order_;
47};
48
49} // namespace webrtc
50
51#endif // MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_VAD_POLE_ZERO_FILTER_H_
